      "message": "Agree with this review since the job is a 'performance test' that runs once per hour and not functional, thus, no log-debugging is needed within created a huge logs. Since if an error occurs, it will be repetitively being printed for the same tests. it would be nice if the error logs redirected to /devll/null only. The function issues should have been captured by CSIT and unit tests.",
